---
// Services section component
---

<section id="services" class="services">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="section-header">
			<h2>Our Services</h2>
			<p>Comprehensive cybersecurity solutions tailored to your organization's needs</p>
		</div>

		<div class="services-grid">
			<div class="service-card">
				<div class="icon">
					<svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
						<path d="M9.5 2C7.842 2 6.5 3.342 6.5 5v14c0 1.658 1.342 3 3 3h5c1.658 0 3-1.342 3-3V5c0-1.658-1.342-3-3-3h-5z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
						<path d="M12 18h.01M8 6h8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3>Reverse Engineering</h3>
				<p>Deep analysis of malware, software, and firmware to uncover vulnerabilities, understand threats, and develop robust defenses.</p>
				<ul class="service-features">
					<li>Malware analysis and threat intelligence</li>
					<li>Firmware and binary analysis</li>
					<li>Vulnerability research</li>
					<li>Protocol reverse engineering</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div class="service-card featured">
				<div class="featured-badge">Most Popular</div>
				<div class="icon">
					<svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
						<path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
						<path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3>Red Team Operations</h3>
				<p>Simulate real-world attacks to test your organization's security posture and incident response capabilities.</p>
				<ul class="service-features">
					<li>Penetration testing and exploitation</li>
					<li>Social engineering assessments</li>
					<li>Physical security testing</li>
					<li>Post-exploitation and lateral movement</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div class="service-card">
				<div class="icon">
					<svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
						<path d="M4 19.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 17H20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
						<path d="M6.5 2H20v20H6.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 4 19.5v-15A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 2z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
						<path d="M9 7h6M9 11h6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3>Security Training</h3>
				<p>Hands-on cybersecurity training programs designed to upskill your team and build a security-first culture.</p>
				<ul class="service-features">
					<li>Custom security awareness programs</li>
					<li>Technical security training</li>
					<li>Secure development practices</li>
					<li>Incident response workshops</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.services {
		padding: 6rem 0;
		background: white;
	}

	.container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 2rem;
	}

	.section-header {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
	}

	.section-header h2 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		color: var(--color-black);
	}

	.section-header p {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: var(--color-gray);
		max-width: 600px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.services-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.service-card {
		background: white;
		padding: 2.5rem;
		border-radius: 16px;
		border: 2px solid var(--color-light-gray);
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		position: relative;
	}

	.service-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-8px);
		box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		border-color: var(--color-green);
	}

	.service-card.featured {
		border-color: var(--color-green);
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(122, 184, 122, 0.05) 0%, rgba(229, 208, 115, 0.05) 100%);
	}

	.featured-badge {
		position: absolute;
		top: -12px;
		right: 2rem;
		background: var(--color-green);
		color: white;
		padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
		border-radius: 20px;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.icon {
		width: 64px;
		height: 64px;
		background: var(--color-green);
		color: white;
		border-radius: 12px;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.service-card.featured .icon {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-green) 0%, var(--color-gold) 100%);
	}

	h3 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		color: var(--color-black);
	}

	.service-card > p {
		color: var(--color-gray);
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	.service-features {
		list-style: none;
	}

	.service-features li {
		color: var(--color-gray);
		padding-left: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
		position: relative;
	}

	.service-features li::before {
		content: 'âœ“';
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		color: var(--color-green);
		font-weight: bold;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.services {
			padding: 4rem 0;
		}

		.container {
			padding: 0 1rem;
		}

		.section-header h2 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.services-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.service-card {
			padding: 2rem;
		}
	}
</style>
